Title: 159: From Developer to Data Scientist
Description:
In this episode of the SuperDataScience Podcast, I chat with the aspiring data scientist, Mike Taveirne. You will hear about the five stages of the data science process for beginners, get valuable tips for people who want to learn and transition to data science, and learn how to apply your data science knowledge to your hobbies and interests.


If you enjoyed this episode, check out show notes, resources, and more at www.superdatascience.com/159
